            "text": "{\"id\":\"chatcmpl-YbjG5XOhlekYblCyUP10gxTD\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1774797623,\"model\":\"kimi-for-coding\",\"choices\":[{\"index\":0,\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Hello\",\"reasoning_content\":\"The user wants me to say hello in one word. The most common one-word greeting is simply \\\"Hello\\\" itself. Other options could be \\\"Hi\\\", \\\"Hey\\\", \\\"Greetings\\\", \\\"Salutations\\\", etc. But the simplest and most direct answer is \\\"Hello\\\".\\n\\nThe user asked for \\\"one word\\\" so I should provide exactly one word without any additional punctuation or explanation, though a period might be acceptable. Actually, looking at the request \\\"Say hello in one word\\\", providing just the word \\\"Hello\\\" is the most appropriate response.\\n\\nWait, I should check if there are any constraints I'm missing. The user wants a one-word greeting. \\\"Hello\\\" is one word. \\\"Hi\\\" is also one word and shorter. But \\\"Hello\\\" is the standard greeting that matches the request most literally.\\n\\nI'll go with \\\"Hello\\\".\"},\"finish_reason\":\"stop\"}],\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":13,\"completion_tokens\":173,\"total_tokens\":186,\"cached_tokens\":13,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":13}}}"
